high_descs: turn left and head for the shelf
pick up the knife
turn around and head for the table
slice the tomato on the table
turn around and head for the microwave
place the knife in the oven
turn around to the table
pick up a slice from the tomato
turn left to the oven
place it to cook and then take it out
turn around to the shelf
place the tomato on the shelf
anns.task_desc: place a cooked tomato  slice on the shelf

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the black end table.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the black end table.
Turn around and cross the room then turn left and face the end of the table.
Cut the tomato into slices.
walk around the left side of the table to the other end of the room and face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk around the table to face the opposite side of the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the table.
walk around the left side of the table to the other end of the room and face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room to face the black end table.
Place the tomato slice on the black end table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of tomato and place it on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the white table, across the kitchen, then turn to your right and go to the black table to the left of the counter.
Pick up the knife to the left of the coffee cup, on the table.
Turn around and go to the right side of the white table, across from you.
Cut the tomato near the edge, on the table, into slices.
Turn to your left and take a few steps, then turn to your right to go around to go around the table, and go straight ahead to the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the far end of the white table, with the sliced tomato near the edge.
Pick up on of the tomato slices, on the table.
Turn to your left, take a few steps, then turn to your right again to go around the table, and walk straight across the kitchen, to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato slice from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, and make a right at the white table to the right of the stove, then go to the small, black table to the right of the counter.
Place the tomato slice on the small black table, between the pump bottle and the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato slice on the table.
